{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"96a4a85bb1","title":"陈伯达等审查交响乐《海港》时的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a1345f356d","index":0,"year":1967,"month":10,"day":9,"articleId":"96a4a85bb1"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"e46e45351b","name":"陈伯达","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"83e7437198","type":"title","text":"陈伯达等审查交响乐《海港》时的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"96a4a85bb1"},{"id":"af56da44ad","type":"authors","text":"陈伯达","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"96a4a85bb1"},{"id":"d616e5f7a8","type":"appellation","text":"〖十月九日晚，伯达、戚本禹、叶群等同志在首都剧场看了中央乐团新创作的第二个交响乐《海港》，看后，伯达同志作了简短指示。〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"96a4a85bb1"},{"id":"b8ec97e08e","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达同志指示：","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"96a4a85bb1"},{"id":"7d7f2ecb1c","type":"paragraph","text":"江青同志最近工作很忙，今天晚上叫我们先来听一听，这个戏，演唱还是很好的，江青同志想听一下，希望能够录下音，交给江青同志。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"96a4a85bb1"},{"id":"0cc4a54804","type":"paragraph","text":"整个戏的场面还是可以的，有的地方机器声太吵，应再静一些。为了慎重起见，还是希望江青同志看过后，再当众演出。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"96a4a85bb1"}],"page":{"id":"6c9764586d","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"96a4a85bb1","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}